data.description: NEW ROOF! NEW POOL EQUIPMENT! TRANSFERABLE HOME WARRANTY! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Mesa, Arizona! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem, perfectly situated on a beautiful corner lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the timeless elegance of a formal living and dining room, creating the ideal space for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories with loved ones. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with a spacious island and a pantry that will delight the chef in your family. With ample counter space and storage, meal preparation becomes a breeze, and the open layout ensures you'll always be part of the conversation, whether you're whipping up a culinary masterpiece or enjoying casual meals. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat that offers a touch of luxury with sliding doors that open to your very own backyard oasis. The ensuite bathroom is equally impressive, providing a spa-like experience with its amenities. One of the standout features of this home is the private pool, a cool haven that's perfect for escaping the Arizona heat or hosting poolside gatherings with friends and family. Enjoy lazy afternoons floating in the water or relax on the pool deck with a good book. And for those with recreational vehicles or outdoor hobbies, an RV gate is an added convenience, offering secure storage and easy access. This home is more than just a house; it's a place where memories are made. With its ideal location in Mesa, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and excellent schools. Make it your home today!
